  - Reuse only components already exposed in Storybook.

  - If a component doesn't exist yet, create a `WIP` story in

    `stories/Design System/Components/` (never in `src/components`).

- **Tokens**

  - Use the values present in

    `stories/Design System/Tokens/` as the official reference.

  - Do not modify or read `lib/constants/tokens.ts` during phase 3.1.

- **Accessibility**

  - Provide at least one story variant with `aria-label`, `tabIndex`, and keyboard focus.

- **Tests**

  - All validations (visual, design, consistency, accessibility) are done via stories.

  - No direct source code verification.

- **Exclusions**

  - No creation or modification in ANY source code directories (`src/`, `app/`, `lib/`, `components/`, `hooks/`, etc.).

  - No addition of new tokens outside Storybook.

  - No testing or preview outside Storybook environment.

